<plot>Journalist Maria Shriver interviews legendary Las Vegas illusionists, Siegfried &amp; Roy, who speak out for the first time since Roy's harrowing ordeal on stage with one of his tigers. The rise to stardom and the legacy of these magical men are cleverly interwoven throughout this highly compelling and thoughtful television hour.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?496290</url></doc>
